<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَمِثَال <span style="color:#008000">(فَعَلَ)</span> المفتوح لَازِما جَلَسَ وقَعَدَ وجَاءَ وقَامَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ومتعدّيا <span style="color:#707070">[٨/ ب]</span> ضَرَبَ وأكَلَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>